        <briefdescription>
<para>Apply uniform external force along the prismatic joint axis to all joints. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Must be applied AFTER <ref refid="classuipc_1_1constitution_1_1AffineBodyPrismaticJoint" kindref="compound">AffineBodyPrismaticJoint</ref> (constitution_uid == 20). The force is a scalar: +f*t applied to body_i, -f*t applied to body_j, where t is the joint tangent direction.</para>
